    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。那即时广播创建时需要走OAuth2认证对吧？未来广播是不是不需要这个额外校验？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "SCHEDULED",
        "PREPARING"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，即时广播涉及实时用户数据拉取，必须用OAuth2。未来广播只是先占位，到临近执行时才做预计算。所以SCHEDULED状态应该能流转到PREPARING，由预计算调度器触发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "SCHEDULED",
        "PREPARING",
        "Pre-computation scheduler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上这条流转线。另外PREPARING阶段要做异步用户获取，成功就到READY，失败应该有个终态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PREPARING",
        "READY",
        "FAILED"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "失败走FAILED，成功到READY。READY之后由激活调度器推进到ACTIVE，这里也要OAuth2校验。还有，管理员随时能取消，SCHEDULED、PREPARING、READY都能转到CANCELLED。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "READY",
        "ACTIVE",
        "CANCELLED",
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Activation scheduler"
