        "ACTIVE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ACTIVE有三种出口：正常到期走EXPIRED，管理员API取消走CANCELLED，还有一种特殊情况——如果是群组广播，DLT事件消费失败会走FAILED。EXPIRED完成后回到ZeroTrust，CANCELLED和FAILED都要落到Security_Firewall做审计隔离。",
